    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps and the model revision of 2025-11-24 occurring after the experimental dataset was frozen on 2025-11-03, the assessment team concluded that the turbulence-coefficient recalibration introduced in the revision was not material to the hemolysis QoI and that the dataset remains valid for supporting the credibility claim. No formal re-validation run was conducted against the revised model build. The decision to accept is predicated on this informal materiality judgement rather than on documented re-validation evidence, constituting the targeted W-EP-03 stale-input-data weakness.",
